@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ansapw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.exp(v1) * 0.30)
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.53) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.68) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.04)))
    tmp = (0.87 * 0.44)
    data[tid] = v0
